The '''2009â10 Washington State Cougars men's basketball team''' represented [[Washington State University]] during the [[2009-10 NCAA Division I men's basketball season]]. The team played its home games on Jack Friel Court at [[Beasley Coliseum]] in [[Pullman, WA|Pullman]], [[Washington (U.S. state)|Washington]]<ref>{{cite web|title= Washington State men's basketball|url=http://wsucougars.cstv.com/sports/m-baskbl/wast-m-baskbl-body.html|work=|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5hLPY5Lz9|archivedate=2009-06-06|deadurl=no|accessdate=2009-03-08}}</ref> and are members of the [[Pacific-10 Conference]]. They finished the season 16&ndash;15, 6&ndash;12 in Pac-10 play and lost in the first round of the [[2010 Pacific-10 Conference Men's Basketball Tournament]]. They were not invited to a post season tournament.
